155
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:36,400
Eu sempre serei seu apoio.

156
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,440
Eu sou o grande Zheng Ze Shou.

157
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,640
Quero dizer, Yuki...

158
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:03,920
